She goes slower than Wanda but both of these create a horror show for students that is known as organic chemistry. Demotivating prof.

rComments: She is a very amiable humble knowledgeable and patient professor.

Excellent prof. Knows her stuff, explains it well. Material might be a little difficult, but as long as you go to class and do practice questions you should be okay. Exams are fair, final was a little tricky but again, if you study you will certainly do well.
